Name: osm-abandoned-railway
Query: railway in ('abandoned') and (tunnel is null or tunnel != 'yes') and (bridge is null or bridge != 'yes')

Name: osm-motorway-highway
Query: highway in ('motorway') and (tunnel is null or tunnel != 'yes') and (bridge is null or bridge != 'yes')

Name: osm-pier-man_made-lines
Query: highway in ('primary') and (tunnel is null or tunnel != 'yes') and (bridge is null or bridge != 'yes')

Name: osm-primary-highway
Query: railway in ('rail', 'light_rail', 'subway') and (tunnel is null or tunnel != 'yes') and (bridge is null or bridge != 'yes') and usage in ('main', 'branch')

Name: osm-rock-natural
Query: highway in ('secondary') and (tunnel is null or tunnel != 'yes') and (bridge is null or bridge != 'yes')

Name: osm-scrub-natural
Query: highway in ('trunk') and (tunnel is null or tunnel != 'yes') and (bridge is null or bridge != 'yes')
